{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4d39796ebc","title":"党，我呼唤......","origin":"1957.6.20北京大学广场编委会编油印版《北大民主墙选辑》","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"452bd20541","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":22,"articleId":"4d39796ebc"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"c5892196e2","name":"林昭"},{"id":"c8c4c23717","name":"（任锋）"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"327e7cf69d","type":"title","text":"党，我呼唤……","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"a8a693e32c","type":"authors","text":"北京大学林昭（任锋）","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"575738a681","type":"paragraph","text":"[注：据钱理群《“五一九文存”序》，任锋即林昭]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"1bb9a7fb12","type":"paragraph","text":"死寂的狰狞的长夜，","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"3082b11115","type":"paragraph","text":"窗外有警车疾驰，","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"c470882663","type":"paragraph","text":"在镣铐的阴影底下，","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"150cbcabe2","type":"paragraph","text":"党，我坚定地呼唤着你。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"933cf837ce","type":"paragraph","text":"当世纪已经更新，","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"f812155ce8","type":"paragraph","text":"碧云中飞扬着红旗，","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"f077448b6b","type":"paragraph","text":"多么巨大的欢乐","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"675680579c","type":"paragraph","text":"党，我狂喜地呼唤着你。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"2dfc98c5dd","type":"paragraph","text":"太阳下我看见黑影，","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"2e38c3a9c5","type":"paragraph","text":"角落里涌漫着邪气，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"5856e6b4d0","type":"paragraph","text":"我惊骇，迷惑而怀疑，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"00f751d584","type":"paragraph","text":"但是，党，我依旧呼唤着你。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"f099b0780e","type":"paragraph","text":"奇怪的谴责像马刀砍来，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"250d960fe3","type":"paragraph","text":"我年青的心伤痕斑斑，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"59107115f1","type":"paragraph","text":"我要母亲，像渔人要水。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"88b441d09b","type":"paragraph","text":"党，我颤动的嘴唇轻轻呼唤。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"eaf2004c32","type":"paragraph","text":"我曾经日夜在痛苦中徘徊，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"c43639a372","type":"paragraph","text":"只觉得寒风刺骨长途漫漫，","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"c242abb380","type":"paragraph","text":"给我一句，一句亲切的话吧，","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"c83297f23f","type":"paragraph","text":"党，我呼唤你时有满怀辛酸！","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"1e62e5babe","type":"paragraph","text":"寂静的深夜我独坐水隈，","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"aad05a52f2","type":"paragraph","text":"水里有死神诱惑的笑颜，","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"e229c96b4d","type":"paragraph","text":"来，它说：你生活中只有暗夜，","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"970d3b3165","type":"paragraph","text":"党，我还想呼唤，心情却已迷乱……","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"b368ab2929","type":"paragraph","text":"今天我又呼唤我的母亲，","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"4e84ab3f01","type":"paragraph","text":"请倾听孩子悲怆的声音，","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"536050a25c","type":"paragraph","text":"先别苛责我的眼泪和激动，","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"fd03b9921d","type":"paragraph","text":"多少次打击伤得我那么深……","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"},{"id":"23070a21c6","type":"paragraph","text":" 57.5.22日","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc"}],"page":{"id":"d7e6e0fea4","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4d39796ebc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}